\mt2 This book is the account of Joel foretelling about many nations conquering the Israeli people and about God restoring them. We call this book  
\mt1 Joel  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1  \add I am\add* \w Joel|strong="H3100"\w*, \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Pethuel|strong="H6602"\w*. \add This is\add* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w message|strong="H1697"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w*.   
\s1 The attack by locusts  
\q1
\v 2 \w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w leaders|strong="H2205"\w* \add of Israel\add*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w everyone|strong="H3605"\w* \w else|strong="H3605"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w lives|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w this|strong="H2063"\w* country, \w listen|strong="H8085"\w* \add to this message\add*!  
