\q1
\v 4  \add I am talking about\add* \w the|strong="H3499"\w* \w locusts|strong="H3218"\w* \w that|strong="H3499"\w* have eaten our crops.  
\q2 \w The|strong="H3499"\w* first swarm \w of|strong="H3499"\w* \w locusts|strong="H3218"\w* came \w and|strong="H3499"\w* cut \add many of the leaves of the crops\add*;  
\q1 then another swarm came \w and|strong="H3499"\w* ate \add the rest of the leaves\add*,  
\q2 then another swarm came hopping along,  
\q1 \w and|strong="H3499"\w* finally another swarm came  
\q2 \w and|strong="H3499"\w* they destroyed \add everything else\add*.   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 \w You|strong="H3588"\w* people \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H6310"\w* \w drunk|strong="H8354"\w*, \w wake|strong="H6974"\w* \w up|strong="H5921"\w*!  
