\v 4 \w You|strong="H6440"\w* \add people of\add* [APO] Tyre \w and|strong="H3068"\w* Sidon \add cities\add* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \add you people of\add* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Philistia \add region\add*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* certainly \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3372"\w* [RHQ] done anything \w to|strong="H3068"\w* harm \w you|strong="H6440"\w*! \add So\add* if \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w are|strong="H3117"\w* trying \w to|strong="H3068"\w* get revenge \w on|strong="H3117"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H1419"\w* quickly get revenge \w on|strong="H3117"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*.  
